title: @OspreyMTEN Finishes Third Day at USTA/ITA Regionals
text: fell in their Round of 16 match 8-4. In the main draw singles, Deautriell fell in his Round of 32 match in the main draw, 6-0, 6-2. Findel-Hawkins advanced to the Round of 16 in the Consolation Draw, winning 6-0, 6-3, before falling 3-6, 7-6(6), 6-2. Also in consolation play was Zuern, who dropped his Round of 32 match 6-4, 6-1. The action continues tomorrow with the fourth day of play from Gainesville.
